# Cloudflare Workers Assets rewrite rules.
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>. Status 200 = rewrite
# (serve the target's content, keep the original URL).
#
# Dynamic client routes aren't prerendered, so a direct hit would
# miss the asset lookup and fall through to the 404 page. Rewrite
# each dynamic tree to its matching prerendered shell; SolidStart's
# client router picks up the real path on hydration.

/studio/:id  /studio  200
